<article class="config-card config-card-soft">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">Downloads</p>
      <h3>Configuracoes da fila</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="config-module-intro">
    <strong>Parametros de transferencia</strong>
    <p>Ajuste como a coleta deve se comportar em volume, repeticoes e tempo limite de tentativa.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="form-grid">
    <label>
      <span>Destino</span>
      <input id="downloadDestinationDir" type="text" value="data/local-acervo" readonly />
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Simultaneos</span>
      <select id="downloadConcurrency">
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2">2</option>
        <option value="3" selected>3</option>
        <option value="4">4</option>
        <option value="5">5</option>
        <option value="8">8</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Tentativas</span>
      <select id="downloadRetryCount">
        <option value="0">0</option>
        <option value="1">1</option>
        <option value="2" selected>2</option>
        <option value="3">3</option>
      </select>
    </label>
    <label>
      <span>Timeout</span>
      <select id="downloadTimeoutMs">
        <option value="15000">15s</option>
        <option value="30000" selected>30s</option>
        <option value="45000">45s</option>
        <option value="60000">60s</option>
      </select>
    </label>
  </div>

  <label class="toggle-line strong-line">
    <input id="downloadOverwrite" type="checkbox" />
    <span>Sobrescrever arquivo existente no destino</span>
  </label>

  <p class="config-note">Os arquivos baixados entram automaticamente no acervo local e passam a abrir pelo link interno quando houver espelho salvo.</p>
</article>
